            <div id="welcome_text">
            <div id="orange_edge"></div>
            	<p>We are changing the coffee game by reinventing both the recipe and the process. We are an all organic, fair trade and plant-based company, on a creatively innovative mission to make the world a better place. We are looking to lead the way as the forerunner of low acid, stomach friendly Koffee. Our unique cold-brew process concentrates more bold flavor and less acidity than your standard brew, while our restructured water brings alive the health benefits of coffee. It’s fun, portable sized bottle is a hit wherever it goes...and it fits just about anywhere!” </p>
